{"tid":830902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又贏！山竹打爆葵涌邨玻璃　房署為街坊著想　免費維修","createTime":"2018-09-21T13:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T15:03:47.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8a851ed1f310363edc6e78c533bdc984b42831c7","tid":830902,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T13:24:45.000Z","msg":"「雖然房署同意今次屬意外，所有房署原裝嘅玻璃窗，<span style=\"color: red;\">都可免費維修</span>。不過，將來若再發生同類情況，就未必可以一樣得到免費維修。」據知，單是葵涌邨，於山竹襲港期間，有近數十間房屋被打爆玻璃。<br />\n<br />\n而房署回覆《香港01》的查詢時，亦指出公屋租戶需自費修葺單位內破損的窗戶玻璃，但因今次超强颱風「山竹」襲港，對不少窗戶造成破損，此並非人為蓄意破壞或不慎使用。經審慎考慮後，房屋署決定酌情處理。若租戶的破損窗戶屬原裝窗戶，會免費更換破損的窗戶玻璃，但不包括租戶已自行安裝的窗戶的租戶。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/238093/%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F-%E5%B1%B1%E7%AB%B9%E6%89%93%E7%88%86%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E9%82%A8%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83-%E6%88%BF%E7%BD%B2%E7%82%BA%E8%A1%97%E5%9D%8A%E8%91%97%E6%83%B3-%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E7%B6%AD%E4%BF%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F238093%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B1%258B%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%2584%258F-%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25AB%25B9%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%2591%25B5%25E6%25B6%258C%25E9%2582%25A8%25E7%258E%25BB%25E7%2592%2583-%25E6%2588%25BF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%259D%258A%25E8%2591%2597%25E6%2583%25B3-%25E5%2585%258D%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E4%25BF%25AE&d=vs7F5PsZ8m7YXihqtHQyZUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=105c023c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/238093/%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F-%E5%B1%B1%E7%AB%B9%E6%89%93%E7%88%86%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E9%82%A8%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83-%E6%88%BF%E7%BD%B2%E7%82%BA%E8%A1%97%E5%9D%8A%E8%91%97%E6%83%B3-%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E7%B6%AD%E4%BF%AE</a>"},{"pid":"882b6e7476c2bf6127d14192ff3e5c58ef7f6969","tid":830902,"uid":5